Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的右手卡迪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有找到银之勇者吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把他找出来,献给我!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我得到银的力量,成为现世的霸王!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把银之勇者找出来!余下的统统杀掉!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是银之勇者,原来是青铜勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好,省得去找的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔导士?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴洛鲁大人,抓到青铜勇者了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极黑之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带那个女孩过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要点些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一杯夫奈卡尔内鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人在旅行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去不像是普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你最好快点离开本城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是巴洛鲁统治的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定听到过他在捕杀战士的风声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是听到这个风声才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到你了,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装做不知道,太冷淡了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们来?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐,无知可是一件很可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是受奴隶商人布安大人委托管理这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好还是不要反抗我们!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌你们这种人了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那最好啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想打吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭婆娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了!都住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想死吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起,弄坏你店里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是常有的事,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐,干的好,来喝一杯如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐,我的名字是蕾姆莉亚,我不喝福斯酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚,你还是快点离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一定会回来报复
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:07:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果传说是真的话,今晚她一定会到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩太强了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从一开始就没指望过你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事情,布安?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大魔导师卡迪大人,我们找到那个银发女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦,她在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她马上就要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看你的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖束手就擒吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于找到你了!杀死爸爸妈妈的仇人了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看你的力量吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔导?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么?!快抓住她!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚库!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚库!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的破坏魔导术居然没起作用!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干的漂亮,卡迪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错,这是银的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要返回巴路萨斯,请巴洛鲁大人赐予力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把那个女孩带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,把她放在兽车上!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连鸟兽一起带回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在做恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定是遇到了什么很可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来,这里是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇泰的牢城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢城?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是被抓来当奴隶的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是蕾姆莉亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是,但是你怎么知道我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见过仙导师大人后你就会了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙导师?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在后面的钟乳洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他从很久以前就在等你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去见他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真的是传说中的勇者吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫蕾姆莉亚女孩居然能抵抗卡迪大人的魔导术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她走之前先尝尝她的味道也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的女人我已经玩够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去带蕾姆莉亚过来!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是蕾姆莉亚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等待你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将古时的传说流传下来是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里一直等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和传说中的勇者见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你听完这流传在卡南这个地方传说就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布安真是精力旺盛,要那么多的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊,我也要好好学学他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一章,第三页
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当金,银,青铜,失去时代的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极黑之翼就会覆盖整个天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把整个世界都笼罩在其阴影之下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔趁人类心灵软弱之际而入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使整个大地成为被神所抛弃的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个银发女孩在哪里?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是你的女儿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她带走!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好疼爱你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉我!这都是为了你女儿好!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银之力量释放之时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青铜将超越金获得神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面就没有记载了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是我要给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个项链是勇者的证物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有当它佩带着勇者身上时,才会发挥出力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股光芒!没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是勇者力量的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的力量是抑制其他勇者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要封印不被解开,时代便不会在转动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是躲在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起,莉安!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布安大人喜欢银发的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就陪陪我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好疼爱你的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快点离开这里,我去救莉安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!住手!放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经乖多了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开,我先上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以这样!别开玩笑了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是对我有不满!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧,莉安?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好,谢谢你,蕾姆莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去大家那里,好让妈妈放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去救其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了,我可等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来这里服侍我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地牢已经打开了,快让这里的人也恢复自由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太天真了,该放下剑的是你,蕾姆莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下你的剑!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里座下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成傀儡后勇者也是很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来人啊!去看看下面的情况!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续跳!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙导师大人,这里很危险,请快到城外去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这云的移动很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙!他来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴路奇萨斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面的情况怎么了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么光芒?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布安大人!奴隶暴动了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴路奇萨斯的雷!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡迪大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴洛鲁大人赐予你魔导之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为了让你玩弄女人吧,布安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把留在自己的身边那是因为!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要亲自监视她,以免她逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡迪!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅,布安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡迪大人,您要做什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡迪!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚!青铜勇者在等着你!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来巴路奇萨斯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来巴路奇萨斯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回巴路奇萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信你的力量,勇敢的去战斗吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就能开拓出属于你自己的道路来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你,请代我向大家问好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚库!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你,剩下的路我自己来就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到大家身边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡迪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经把她引入巴路奇萨斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真的是银之勇者吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还没有完全觉醒,不过我认为没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就把她引入这里的王座之室!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青铜勇者麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你好好来欣赏这个助兴节目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银之勇者!让这红光来引导你到王座之室吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个螺旋的走廊是通向王座之室的唯一道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作快点吧,这里就要崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.30,0:23:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那道光芒的确是银之勇者,没错!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话我的宿愿就能完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蕾姆莉亚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青铜勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你活着就是为了引银之勇者到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是引蕾姆莉亚的饵!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚!不要过来!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.33,0:23:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡迪!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银之勇者!我的使命结束了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也可以如你所愿,在这里和你决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意!你欠我的帐还没有还呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.35,0:24:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.69,0:24:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡迪…变成了手!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.39,0:24:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡迪是我的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.10,0:25:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银之勇者,你也跟青铜勇者一起成为我力量的一部分吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.41,0:25:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.71,0:25:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚!打倒他!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.21,0:25:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能压制巴洛鲁的只有你的银之力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.72,0:25:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.42,0:25:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.12,0:25:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴洛鲁!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.74,0:25:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了!快把你的力量交出来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.04,0:25:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚,快点醒过来!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.15,0:25:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.65,0:25:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开蕾姆莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.46,0:26:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是什么力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.07,0:26:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.67,0:26:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.77,0:26:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能打破我的符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.18,0:26:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越来越想要你的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.38,0:26:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云…时代开始转动了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.19,0:26:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者的战斗开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.79,0:26:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴路奇萨斯渐渐远去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.81,0:26:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一套!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.21,0:26:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么,精彩的还在后面呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.81,0:26:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在知道反抗我的下场了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.82,0:26:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是绝对不会输给你的!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.12,0:27:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.83,0:27:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下来该怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.54,0:27:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.35,0:27:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.26,0:27:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.57,0:27:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏该结束了!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.19,0:28:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴洛鲁!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.00,0:28:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你失手了,巴洛鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.85,0:28:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.32,0:28:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.32,0:28:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.03,0:28:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢,以为这点程度的伤害就能打倒我!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.33,0:28:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.94,0:28:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.04,0:29:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物?!你是不会了解的!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所背负着金之勇者的使命,到底有多么的痛苦!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.95,0:29:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类为了排除异族
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.65,0:29:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我丢入魔导森林
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.96,0:29:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我痛恨人类,怨恨他们
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.96,0:29:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我从绝望和黑暗只中解救出来的是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.97,0:29:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是魔导的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.87,0:29:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那刻起我就发誓要征服世界统治伪善的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.38,0:29:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓过!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.69,0:29:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不再是人类了!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.19,0:29:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化为我的力量吧,蕾姆莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.70,0:30:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你得逞的!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.00,0:30:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就必须去死!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.73,0:30:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还能站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.63,0:30:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.23,0:30:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次你死定了!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.85,0:30:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.47,0:31:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你,蕾姆莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.48,0:31:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要平安回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.38,0:31:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安…伯母…大家…仙导师…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.10,0:31:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,我可以吸收银之力量了!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.10,0:31:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信你的力量,勇敢的去战斗吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.12,0:32:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.54,0:32:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.95,0:32:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.97,0:32:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们两个复活了!怎么会有这种事情!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.17,0:32:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种将力量用于自己的野心的人是不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.57,0:32:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为金之勇者竟然想征服世界!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.48,0:33:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴!你们真的相信那个瞎老头的预言吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.28,0:33:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类和龙只有我暂时的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.89,0:33:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就让你见识一下我真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.69,0:33:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴路奇萨斯横越天空
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.10,0:33:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将大地燃尽的时刻已经到来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.60,0:33:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的末日已经到来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.93,0:33:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头巨人!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.23,0:33:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴洛鲁最后的王牌巴路奇萨斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.94,0:34:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢!在将大地燃尽之前
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.34,0:34:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会先收拾掉你们的!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.26,0:34:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.26,0:34:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.29,0:34:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚库!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.50,0:35:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真的没有问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.01,0:35:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有办法看的到\N能做的只有相信她,等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.31,0:35:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚库,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.02,0:35:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区一个人类竟敢挑战我巴路奇萨斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.32,0:35:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.03,0:35:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不认为你有你自己想的那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.33,0:35:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我知道你的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.33,0:35:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你额头上的眼睛!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.84,0:35:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.85,0:35:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.47,0:36:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的剑是无法伤害他的魔眼的!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.80,0:36:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔眼就是他本身最大的弱点!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.80,0:36:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.41,0:36:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银之力量释放之时
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.41,0:36:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青铜将超越金获得神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.71,0:36:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.14,0:37:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在再生!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.87,0:37:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想飞起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.87,0:37:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶,该怎么办才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.18,0:38:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.49,0:38:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾姆莉亚!\N什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.69,0:38:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看!
